{"about_the_game":"True Hate - is an thrilling acrobatic platformer with an unusual storyline, Packed in colorful, hand-drawn graphics. Make your way to your goal through a dark forest overgrown with thorns, deep caves filled with lava, blooming jungles, mysterious ruins and a hot desert. Jump over abysses filled with boiling lava and sharp spikes, dodge lasers and fireballs, look for secret exits and remember - absolutely everything in this magical world wants to kill you! Try to think fast, be extremely attentive. It all depends only on you. Get ready to face unpredictable and deadly obstacles that only experience and willpower will help you overcome, and if you lose, you'll have to go back to the beginning of the story.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A game that will teach you patience (or drive you crazy)<br></li><li> Travel to different locations and climatic zones of the fantastic 2D world drawn by hand.<br></li><li> Simple and convenient game control. Success depends only on your skills.<br></li><li> You can play with the controller<br></li><li> The plot may seem strange to you and not particularly logical, but it is unlikely that you saw something like that somewhere else.<br></li><li> Difficult obstacles, many of which will surprise you, danger lurks where you least expect, and the exit from the level is not always where you hope to find it.<br></li><li> Various and pleasant music, especially for you to relax if you lose control (believe - you will lose control)<br></li><li> Deduce your sense of anxiety to a whole new level</li></ul><br>Add to your wishlist so as not to miss the release and discounts!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385700/extras/availablegif.gif?t=1681547363\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Across the forest","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1385700/baf59dc8576bccb89c333bdd5449a5273